casebody.data:
Richard B. ROEDERER, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Joanne J. ROEDERER, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D16-2214 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 30, 2017 SALTER, FERNANDEZ and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Following review of appellant's response, it is ordered that appellee's renewed motion to dismiss appeal is granted, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed.
